data.description: Enjoy this beautiful custom-built and meticulously maintained  4 bd 2.5 bath home W/ FINISHED BASEMENT and many upgrades & extras! With a flowing layout, an office right off the entry, large great room and kitchen with an extended island leaves plenty of room for entertainment. Massive primary bedroom and loft upstairs for even more privacy and space. Downstairs features a custom-built theatre and living space w/ surround sound speakers, a 4rth bedroom, and even a space to add another full bathroom already roughed-in! Enjoy the pond view and summer nights from your spacious concrete patio with family and friends. Property Website, Video, & 3D Tour in listing. Welcome Home.
